Rocket is a 5 year old Boston Terrier. He&nbsp;is a typical terrier with lots of energy but loves attention. As you can see from his pic, he enjoys life and always wears a smile, He gets along with kids and dogs. He is crate trained but was a mostly outdoor dog in his prior home, so he will need house training. If he was inside he was in a crate, never loose. He is working on his housebreaking and doing good with consistency.
&nbsp;
